         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0009"/>Herrn</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168940">XVIII. Spöttelga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>se 7</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs>.</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><del rend="strikethrough">Ge</del><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb41240"><foreign xml:lang="it">Austria</foreign></rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03236-1"/><foreign xml:lang="it"><hi rend="pre-print">Sul <rs type="place" ref="#pmb90490">lago</rs>.</hi></foreign><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03236-1">Italienisch: auf dem See. Zu sehen
                  ist der <rs type="place" ref="#pmb90490">Como See</rs> mit einem Boot mit
                  Sonnendach, vier Rudern und zwei Männern, die diese stehend bedienen.</note></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="left"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0010"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb91936">Tremezzo</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date when="1905-09-08">8. Sept.</date></dateline></opener><p>Herzliche Grüße Dir, <salute>lieber Freund,</salute> und Deiner <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb2173">Frau</rs>! <lb/><signed>Paul Goldmann.</signed></p></div>
